OL,3,CPolice hunt for four men who robbed
OL,4,Cand assaulted pensioner, 74, in his
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FDetectives are searching for four men
OL,8,Fwho robbed and assaulted a pensioner
OL,9,Fin his home in North Lanarkshire.
OL,11,FPolice Scotland said a 74-year-old was
OL,12,Fthreatened in his home on Clydesdale
OL,13,FStreet, Motherwell by the group at
OL,14,Faround 2.45am on Sunday. The men went
OL,15,Fon to steal a VW Transporter Van,
OL,16,Fwhich contained electrical tools.
OL,18,FThe force said the men were wearing
OL,19,Fdark coloured clothing and concealed
OL,20,Ftheir faces. They were also wearing
OL,21,Fgloves and spoke with local accents.
