OL,7,FOfficers are continuing to carry out
OL,8,Fdoor-to-door inquiries and will be
OL,9,Freviewing CCTV footage. The four men
OL,10,Fwere hanging around in the street
OL,11,Fbefore entering the house, Police
OL,12,FScotland said.
OL,14,F"The motive for this attack is unknown
OL,15,Fand it's imperative we trace those
OL,16,Fresponsible," said Detective Constable
OL,17,FSaajan Learie.
