OL,7,F"I am appealing to anyone in the area
OL,8,Fwho may have seen or heard something
OL,9,Fto get in touch with us. Your
OL,10,Finformation could prove vital in our
OL,11,Finquiries.
OL,13,F"I would also urge people with dash
OL,14,Fcams and doorbell recording equipment
OL,15,Fto check their footage, there may be
OL,16,Fimages relevant to our investigation."
OL,18,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,19,Fcall Police Scotland via 101, quoting
OL,20,Fincident number 0505 of Sunday April
OL,21,F20.
